                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "class": "text-base md:text-xl tracking-wider font-extralight uppercase ",
                    "value": "Nestled in the heart of Ticino, Switzerland, 'Val Bavona' is a realm where nature’s raw power meets human resilience"
                }
            ]
            
        },
        {
            "type": "richtext",
            "text": [
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "class": "text-base md:text-lg tracking-wider font-light  ",
                    "value": "With colossal boulders, towering rock faces, and a wilderness untouched by time, this valley invites visitors to step into a world shaped by glaciers and nurtured by ancient traditions. Here, amidst the rugged terrain, humans have carved out a life—building meadows, fields, and homes in the shadow of sheer cliffs. In this post, discover the untamed beauty, cultural treasures, and outdoor adventures that make Bavona Valley an unmissable destination."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
