                    "value": "(May to October)"
                },
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": ", when trails are clear, waterfalls are at their peak, and the weather is ideal for outdoor activities. The valley is particularly beautiful in the fall when the larch trees turn golden, creating a stunning contrast against the rugged landscape. Winter is also a magical time to visit, with snow-covered peaks and a peaceful atmosphere. However, "
                },
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "class": "font-bold",
