                    "value": "Bavona Valley is a hiker’s paradise, with a network of trails that wind through the rugged landscape, offering stunning views of the surrounding mountains and valleys. From leisurely walks to challenging hikes, there are routes for all skill levels, making it the perfect destination for outdoor enthusiasts. Some popular hikes include "
