                    "value": "Foroglio Waterfall loop",
                    "url": "https://www.ticino.ch/en/hike/details/Foroglio-Caln%C3%A8gia-Foroglio/33120527.html?morf=274485e6-4fca-4603-9daa-24c44fd41240"
                },
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": ", and the "
                },
                {
                    "type": "link",
                    "target":"_blank",
                    "value": "San Carlo to Bignasco hike.",
