            "titlelevel": 3,
            "text": [
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": "Explore Bavona Valley on two wheels with cycling and mountain biking adventures that take you through the valley’s scenic landscapes. From leisurely rides along quiet country roads to adrenaline-pumping descents on mountain trails, "
