        },
        {
            "type": "richtext",
            "title": "Nature Walks",
            "titlelevel": 3,
            "text": [
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": "For a more relaxed outdoor experience, take a nature walk through Bavona Valley’s pristine wilderness. Wander along meandering paths, through lush forests, and beside crystal-clear streams, immersing yourself in the sights and sounds of nature. Keep an eye out for local wildlife, including chamois, ibex, and marmots, as you explore the valley’s diverse ecosystems. Nature walks are a great way to connect with the natural world and experience the beauty of Bavona Valley at a leisurely pace."
                }
            ]
